name: Alice Night Party Dress Up
description:
Do you like to be aware of the latest fashions?
Let's dress Alice with the latest fashion. She must be cute for a night party. Choose nice dresses or pants, some heels, and many other accessories, that every girl should use. She's going to be the prom queen.
There is a great variety of suits to combine as you like.

- A lot of dresses
- many tops and jackets
- many hairstyles, pants, skirts, shoes and more

Do you want to be a fashion designer?
Use your creativity to put together the best combinations.

Be a fashion designer and have fun with our dress up games for girls.

Dress up games for free.
